snippet.textDisplay:
Thank you so much for all your support and praise! It truly means a lot to me... I dreamt that some day I might be able to sing with my father... Never thought that my debut would be with him that too on such a huge platform with so many great people supporting us... I'm so grateful for that... I Wanna Fly was definitely my debut but it meant so much more than that with the message that it passed with it... The relationship I share with my father is extremely extremely special to me and through that song we tried to share a small part of it and 'inspire' other people... 

I still have a long way to go but this support inspires me more! Thank you once again! 

~Brianna Sharmilee Supriyo
snippet.textOriginal:

The relationship I share with my father is extremely extremely special to me and through that song we tried to share a small part of it and 'inspire' other people... 

I still have a long way to go but this support inspires me more! Thank you once again! 

~Brianna Sharmilee Supriyo
